About Us
Sona Foods is an ethnic indian grocery wholesale distribution firm established in 2016. Our main leading Brands are "SAFAL" & "VERKA".

 
 
 






Services
What We Do.
We are a subsidiary of Verka Foods and are based in canada. We supply  premium quality products from Canada , USA , Dubai , India and China.
 
 





Belief
We only believe in the best quality products which is the reason we ensurte safe delievery and a provide 100 % returns policy for our consumers.

 



Managing
Ravi Chawla has an extensive experience of wholesale supplying from India, China & Dubai which has led him to put his steps further in USA: Which is now our prime consumer market.

 



Products
"SAFAL" is our main brand. 
